      "instruction": "<p>Sprinkle the shredded <strong>mozzarella</strong> over the <strong>vegetables</strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p>\n<p>Top with the <strong>olives</strong></p>\n<p>Return the <strong>topped naan</strong> to the oven for 10-15 min or until the cheese has melted and started to brown – this is your <strong>roasted vegetable flatbread</strong></p>",
